These are Puzzles for 7x3 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-2-1::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: 7up, mirinda, soy-milk
There are 3 different favourite colors: aquamarine, brown, black
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: orchid, amaryllis, daffodil
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: time-travel, martial-arts, romance
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: country, d&b, dubstep
There are 3 different nationalities: colombian, german, italian
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: siglo, prince, bongani
 1. the siglo-smoker is the german##1
 2. the bongani-smoker is the person watching romance movies##1
 3. the person drinking soy-milk is between the italian and the person drinking mirinda##2
 4. the fan of d&b is on the left of the colombian##1
 5. the person watching martial-arts movies is the person who likes black##1
 6. the person who growsdaffodil is the colombian##1
 7. the person who growsdaffodil is on the left of the person who likes aquamarine##1
 8. the prince-smoker is on the left of the fan of country##1
 9. the siglo-smoker is on the left of the person watching martial-arts movies##1
10. the person who growsamaryllis is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |       3       |
| Beverage      | mirinda    | soy-milk   | 7up           |
| Color          | brown       | black    | aquamarine         |
| Flower         | amaryllis    | daffodil  | orchid        |
| Movie-Genre           | time-travel | martial-arts   | romance      |
| Music-Genre   | d&b        | dubstep    | country       |
| Nationality   | german     | colombian  | italian       |
| Cigar         | siglo     | prince | bongani |

