.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-2-2::.
City: london, marseilles, boston
The people have 3 different hobbies: fishing, baking, reading
There are 3 different favourite colors: mauve, coral, lilac
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: metal, punk, rock
There are 3 different nationalities: australian, british, dutch
3 different pets are kept: dog, horse, pony
The people have 3 different jobs:  librarian, journalist, videographer
 1. the owner of the pony is the british##1
 2. the owner of the pony is the person who likes lilac##1
 3. the person who likes lilac is on the right of the owner of the dog##1
 4. the librarian is between the person traveling to marseilles and the person traveling to london##2
 5. the dutch is on the far left##1
 6. the person traveling to marseilles is the fan of metal##1
 7. the fan of punk is on the left of the videographer##1
 8. the person who's hobby is fishing is the person who likes mauve##1
 9. the person who likes lilac is on the right of the fan of rock##1
10. the owner of the pony is on the left of the person who's hobby is reading##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |       3       |
| City      | london   | boston    | marseilles         |
| Hobby          | fishing    | baking | reading          |
| Color   | mauve  | lilac  | coral     |
| Music-Genre   | rock       | punk      | metal         |
| Nationality   | dutch      | british   | australian    |
| Pet           | dog        | pony      | horse         |
| Job         | journalist | librarian  | videographer |

