The people have 3 different hobbies: fishing, magic-tricks, skydiving
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: rose, bellflower, poppy
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: folk, pop, r&b
There are 3 different nationalities: egyptian, indian, russian
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: july, october, december
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: tiparillo, ritmeester, game
 1. the person driving the subway is the person who's birthday is in october##1
 2. the russian is the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
 3. the person who growsrose is the person driving the bus##1
 4. the person who growsbellflower is the person who's birthday is in october##1
 5. the ritmeester-smoker is on the left of the game-smoker##1
 6. the person who growsbellflower is on the left of the game-smoker##1
 7. the person who's hobby is skydiving is between the indian and the fan of r&b##2
 8. the indian is on the left of the fan of folk##1
 9. the person who's birthday is in october is on the right of the tiparillo-smoker##1
10. the person who's birthday is in december is on the right of the person driving the subway##1
11. the indian is the person driving the bus##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |      3       |
| Transport          | bus      | subway      | boat      |
| Hobby         | fishing   | skydiving | magic-tricks |
| Flower   | rose | bellflower    | poppy          |
