 3. the game-smoker is on the left of the person watching sports movies##1
 4. the person who growsazalea is on the right of the person who growsdaisy##1
 5. the person who growsdaisy is between the person watching disaster movies and the person driving the motorbike##2
 6. the person driving the van is on the right of the person playing mah-jongg##1
 7. the person who growsdaisy is the person playing whist##1
 8. the musician is the game-smoker##1
 9. the person driving the van is between the musician and the social-worker##2
10. the malaysian is on the left of the egyptian##1

.:: Answer ::.
