.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-2-5::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: 7up, juice, water
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: swisher, bongani, fonseca
The people have 3 different jobs:  engineer, journalist, photographer
The people have 3 different hobbies: filmmaking, dancing, cooking
There are 3 different nationalities: thai, indian, turkish
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: lacrosse, swimming, weightlifting
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: western, horror, romance
 1. the bongani-smoker is on the left of the person watching romance movies##1
 2. the person watching western movies is on the left of the thai##1
 3. the person drinking water is the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
 4. the person drinking juice is on the far right##1
 5. the person who's sport is weightlifting is between the person who's sport is swimming and the person who's hobby is dancing##2
 6. the person who's sport is weightlifting is between the person who's sport is lacrosse and the turkish##2
 7. the person watching western movies is between the fonseca-smoker and the person drinking 7up##2
 8. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the right of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
 9. the journalist is on the right of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
10. the engineer is the fonseca-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |       2       |     3      |
| Beverage      | 7up          | water         | juice      |
| Cigar          | swisher     | bongani         | fonseca |
| Job           | photographer | journalist    | engineer   |
| Hobby   | filmmaking        | cooking          | dancing        |
| Nationality           | turkish        | indian         | thai      |
| Sport         | swimming     | weightlifting | lacrosse   |
| Movie-Genre     | horror    | western          | romance       |

