There are 3 different nationalities: american, indonesian, polish
3 different games are played: go, canasta, snooker
The people have 3 different jobs:  dressmaker, writer, photographer
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: vegafina, bluemaster, old-henry
 1. the photographer is in the middle##1
 2. the person drinking fanta is in the middle##1
 3. the polish is on the right of the person who's hobby is drawing##1
 4. the person who's hobby is singing is the art-deco house##1
 5. the vegafina-smoker is on the right of the polish##1
 6. the person playing snooker is on the left of the art-deco house##1
 7. the old-henry-smoker is between the person drinking almond-milk and the american##2
 8. the craftsman house is on the right of the dressmaker##1
 9. the art-deco house is the vegafina-smoker##1
10. the person playing snooker is on the left of the person playing canasta##1
11. the vegafina-smoker is the american##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3     |
| Beverage      | almond-milk | fanta      | tea      |
| Hobby         | drawing     | hiking     | singing  |
| House   | townhouse | craftsman  | art-deco |
| Nationality   | indonesian  | polish     | american |
| Game           | go        | snooker | canasta     |
| Job         | dressmaker    | photographer | writer   |
| Cigar     | bluemaster        | old-henry        | vegafina   |

