.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-2-18::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: fanta, juice, milk
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: april, march, february
There are 3 different nationalities: german, polish, indonesian
The people have 3 different jobs:  dressmaker, manager, musician
House: futuristic, cape-cod, wooden
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: dubstep, blues, d&b
The people use 3 different means of transport: helicopter, ship, skateboard
1. the person drinking juice is on the left of the musician##1
2. the person driving the skateboard is on the right of the person who's birthday is in february##1
3. the person who's birthday is in march is on the left of the dressmaker##1
4. the fan of dubstep is between the futuristic house and the manager##2
5. the person who's birthday is in february is between the musician and the indonesian##2
6. the polish is on the right of the person who's birthday is in february##1
7. the fan of blues is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
8. the person driving the helicopter is on the left of the person drinking milk##1
9. the cape-cod house is on the left of the dressmaker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |     3      |
| Beverage      | fanta      | juice      | milk       |
| Birthday          | march      | february    | april   |
| Nationality         | indonesian    | german     | polish     |
| Job           | manager    | dressmaker | musician   |
| House   | cape-cod    | wooden    | futuristic       |
| Music-Genre         | d&b | dubstep      | blues    |
| Transport     | ship       | helicopter | skateboard |

