.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-2-19::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: coffee, cola, fanta
There are 3 different favourite colors: coral, lavender, lilac
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: november, january, july
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: animation, scientific, superhero
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: electronic, jazz, reggae
3 different games are played: billiard, bridge, chess
The people have 3 different jobs:  pilot, engineer, paramedic
1. the engineer is the person who's birthday is in january##1
2. the person playing bridge is on the right of the person watching animation movies##1
3. the person playing chess is on the right of the person playing bridge##1
4. the person watching superhero movies is on the right of the paramedic##1
5. the person who likes lavender is between the person drinking fanta and the person who's birthday is in november##2
6. the person who likes lilac is on the right of the fan of reggae##1
7. the person drinking coffee is on the right of the fan of jazz##1
8. the pilot is the person watching superhero movies##1
9. the person who's birthday is in november is on the right of the person who's birthday is in july##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |      3       |
| Beverage      | fanta       | coffee     | cola         |
| Color          | coral     | lavender      | lilac     |
| Birthday         | january | july    | november      |
| Movie-Genre   | animation   | scientific | superhero    |
| Music-Genre   | jazz        | reggae     | electronic   |
| Game         | billiard     | bridge | chess |
| Job     | engineer     | paramedic       | pilot    |

