.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-2-20::.
House: modern, cottage, ranch-style
There 3 different types of food: broccoli, spinach, zucchini
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: bongani, alhambra, davidoff
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: tulip, poppy, sunflower
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: august, december, july
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: baseball, basketball, cycling
The people use 3 different means of transport: car, jet-ski, roller
1. the modern house is the person eating zucchini##1
2. the person driving the roller is the person who's sport is baseball##1
3. the bongani-smoker is between the ranch-style house and the person who's birthday is in july##2
4. the person who growstulip is on the left of the person driving the roller##1
5. the person who's birthday is in august is on the left of the person who's sport is cycling##1
6. the person driving the jet-ski is on the left of the person driving the roller##1
7. the alhambra-smoker is the person eating broccoli##1
8. the person who's birthday is in july is on the left of the person who's birthday is in august##1
9. the person who growspoppy is between the person eating broccoli and the person driving the car##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |    3     |
| House      | cottage    | modern       | ranch-style      |
| Food          | broccoli   | zucchini   | spinach  |
| Cigar           | alhambra  | bongani | davidoff    |
| Flower   | tulip   | poppy     | sunflower  |
| Birthday           | july     | august        | december |
| Sport         | basketball | baseball   | cycling  |
| Transport     | jet-ski    | roller     | car      |

 